select top 1

	when birthday is not null then birthday

end birthday_1,
case 
	when bmi is not null then bmi 
	when height >0 and weight>0 then Convert(decimal(8,2),(weight*10000)/(height*height)	)

DATEDIFF(week,lastmenstrualperiod,getdate()) lastweek,
DATEDIFF(day,lastmenstrualperiod,getdate())%7 lastday,

isnull(trafficflow,0) +isnull(naturalabortion,0) +isnull(odinopoeia,0) +isnull(qwetimes,0) as exceptionpreghistory,
isnull(trafficflow,0) +isnull(naturalabortion,0) as abortionpreghistory,

Convert(decimal(8,1),(DATEDIFF(DY, pregestationdate,lastmenstrualperiod)*1.0 / 365)) pregestationyear,

,* from PregnantInfo where (status = '0' and id = #dataitems.pregid#) ) T","conn":"location_preg"},{"id":3,"text":"孕期内检验结果","name":"alllabresult","sql":"select * from (
